:name: Cortex-R52 UART Hello World
:description: Runs a Hello World demo binary on Cortex-R52 with UART output.

using sysbus

# Create machine
mach create "R52"

# Load platform description for Cortex-R52
machine LoadPlatformDescription @platforms/cpus/cortex-r52.repl

# Path to your ELF file
$bin?=@C:/RENODE/HelloWorld/hello.elf

# Open UART0 analyzer
showAnalyzer uart0

# Define a macro so you can reload and rerun easily
macro reset """
    sysbus LoadELF $bin
    cpu Reset
"""

# Run the reset macro (load ELF and reset CPU)
runMacro $reset

# Start simulation
start







